; Swimnerd FinishLynx Integration Script
; Copyright (c) 2026 Swimnerd
;
; Network/TCP Settings: -1,0.0.0.0,1024
; Serial Settings (if needed): 9600,8,N,1
;
; This script outputs race results from FinishLynx to Swimnerd Live software
; in a simple pipe-delimited format for easy parsing.
;
; Written by: Tim (OpenClaw AI Assistant)
; Date: 2026-03-30
; Version: 1.0
;
; Notes:
;  - Lines starting with ; are comments
;  - \0d\0a = CRLF (carriage return + line feed)
;  - %s = variable placeholder
;  - Group codes (\10-\17) define data type
;  - Variable codes (\00-\0f) define specific field

;;Initialization
; Sent once when FinishLynx connects to Swimnerd
; This helps Swimnerd detect the connection
\10\00SWIMNERD_INIT|v1.0\0d\0a

;;TimeRunning
; Sent while race clock is running
; Format: RUNNING|MM:SS.HH
\11\00RUNNING|
\11\01%s\0d\0a

;;TimeStopped
; Sent when race clock stops
; Format: STOPPED|MM:SS.HH
\11\00STOPPED|
\11\01%s\0d\0a

;;TimeUpdate
; Sent periodically while clock is running (every second)
; Format: UPDATE|MM:SS.HH
\11\00UPDATE|
\11\01%s\0d\0a

;;ResultsHeader
; Sent once before any results are sent
; Format: START_RESULTS|Event|EventNum|Heat|Participants|Official
\13\00START_RESULTS|
\13\02%s|
\13\04%s|
\13\06%s|
\13\08%s|
\13\01%s\0d\0a

;;Result
; Sent once for each finisher
; Format: RESULT|Place|Lane|Id|Name|Team|Time|Delta|ReacTime
\14\00RESULT|
\14\01%s|
\14\02%s|
\14\03%s|
\14\04%s|
\14\05%s|
\14\06%s|
\14\07%s|
\14\0c%s\0d\0a

;;ResultsTrailer
; Sent once after all results
; Format: END_RESULTS
\13\00END_RESULTS\0d\0a

;;Wind
; Sent when wind reading is available (track events)
; Format: WIND|+1.2 or WIND|-0.5
\12\00WIND|
\12\01%s\0d\0a

;;Message
; Sent for custom messages
; Format: MESSAGE|Text
\16\00MESSAGE|
\16\01%s\0d\0a

;;StartListHeader
; Sent before start list (pre-race entries)
; Format: START_LIST|Event|EventNum|Heat
\13\00START_LIST|
\13\02%s|
\13\04%s|
\13\06%s\0d\0a

;;StartList
; Sent for each pre-race entry
; Format: ENTRY|Lane|Id|Name|Team
\14\00ENTRY|
\14\02%s|
\14\03%s|
\14\04%s|
\14\05%s\0d\0a

;;StartListTrailer
; Sent after start list
; Format: END_LIST
\13\00END_LIST\0d\0a
